definitions.definition: A village in Exelby, Leeming and Londonderry parish, North Yorkshire , England , previously in Hambleton district ( OS grid ref SE2989 ) .
A settlement in Oxenhope parish, Metropolitan Borough of Bradford , West Yorkshire , England ( OS grid ref SE0434 ) .
A suburb of Perth , Western Australia .
